OL,3,CPostmistress whose life was nearly
OL,4,Cruined by Horizon returns to Post
OL,5,COffice
OL,7,FReporter Lee Comley was in Handsworth
OL,8,Fin Birmingham when the doors to Roopie
OL,9,FGill's Post Office opened.
OL,11,FA former sub-postmistress who at one
OL,12,Fpoint thought about ending her life
OL,13,Fafter being wrongly accused of theft
OL,14,Fhas returned to work - at the same
OL,15,Fbranch she left 15 years ago.
OL,17,FRooprit Gill - known as 'Roopie' -
OL,18,Flost her money, home and car when she
OL,19,Fwas accused of stealing money amid the
OL,20,Fnational Horizon scandal.
