OL,3,CPostmistress whose life was nearly
OL,4,Cruined by Horizon returns to Post
OL,5,COffice
OL,7,FShe was dismissed from running the
OL,8,FPost Office at the Wattville Road
OL,9,Fstore in the Handsworth area of
OL,10,FBirmingham. It was a business which
OL,11,Fher father had bought in 1976 and
OL,12,Fhanded down to her.
OL,14,FBut she continued to work at the
OL,15,Fconvenience store and now, after weeks
OL,16,Fof training she's back to take over
OL,17,Fher family's business.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/6
