OL,3,CPostmistress whose life was nearly
OL,4,Cruined by Horizon returns to Post
OL,5,COffice
OL,7,FHe said: "She's the first postmistress
OL,8,For postmaster that was affected by the
OL,9,FHorizon scandal to have come back as a
OL,10,Fpostmistress, I think it's an enormous
OL,11,Fmoment.
OL,13,F"For her to put her trust back in the
OL,14,FPost Office is incredible, and it's
OL,15,Fsomething that we need now to back
OL,16,Fthat up and fulfil that trust."
OL,18,FMembers of the local community have
OL,19,Fstuck by Roopie throughout the years,
OL,20,Fand were excited for her new start
