OL,3,CPostmistress whose life was nearly
OL,4,Cruined by Horizon returns to Post
OL,5,COffice
OL,7,FRoopie had been a sub-postmaster for
OL,8,Ffive years when she was suspended. She
OL,9,Fwent to court facing charges of theft
OL,10,Fand false accounting, and was later
OL,11,Fremoved from her role.
OL,13,FHer father saw the impact the Horizon
OL,14,Fscandal had on his daughter, but never
OL,15,Flived to see her name cleared.
OL,17,FNext year marks the 50th anniversary
OL,18,Fof him buying the business.
